{"tid":1170058,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"不要把太多的等待放在別人身上","createTime":"2019-05-24T18:34:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-24T19:00:04.000Z","uid":86602,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"31dc552df3f09b412a1d2696034fd77dbb431da3","tid":1170058,"uid":86602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T18:34:05.000Z","msg":"等一個人來了解你，等一個人主動靠近你。<br />\n等你喜歡的人也剛好喜歡上你。<br />\n這些都是可遇不可求的事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n遇到壞情緒的時候偶爾學會自我消解和面對，<br />\n不要總希望有人可以無時無刻安慰你，等不到時又只剩失望。<br />\n<br />\n追求熱愛的事物也好，努力搵錢去買自己喜歡的東西也好，讓自己的生活充實。<br />\n又或是等一場電影，夏日時份等待黃昏的一絲清涼，買一件心愛的毛衣等待冬天的來臨。<br />\n<br />\n希望大家的所有的等待都如約而至。<br />\n<br />\n想被愛，先好好愛自己呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"331928a3115bfa4a47873a1cbae2c52d18d6697d","tid":1170058,"uid":28741,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T18:36:29.000Z","msg":"多謝你的正能量"},{"pid":"41453235dd974aa7e447360469a452aafb808818","tid":1170058,"uid":86602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"331928a3115bfa4a47873a1cbae2c52d18d6697d","tid":1170058,"uid":28741,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T18:36:29.000Z","msg":"多謝你的正能量"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T18:42:22.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7b767292135dbb6a97d41fbed29fadf6c4ac96a","tid":1170058,"uid":219216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T19:00:04.000Z","msg":"暗戀，正確嗎"}]}